·	Location: To provide accurate Salat and Iqamah times and detect when you are at a mosque to automatically enable or disable silent mode. 
·	Notifications: To deliver Adhan alerts, reminders, and prayer alarms. 
·	Network Data: Fetches prayer times from our API to ensure accuracy.
Data: This app does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information but third-party services (AdMob) do.
