Battery Optimization:Continuous location tracking may increase battery usage. The app is optimized to minimize battery impact while maintaining accurate prayer times and mosque detection.
User Control:
·	You can manually set your location instead of auto-detection. 
·	Notifications and location permissions can be turned off at any time. 
·	All personal data is used solely for prayer functionality and is not shared with third parties. 
Security:All data is stored locally.

# SalahMate Data Deletion Policy

SalahMate does not require users to create an account and does not store personal user data on external servers.

All app settings and preferences are stored locally on the user's device.

Users can delete all app data at any time by:

1. Uninstalling the SalahMate application from their device, or
2. Clearing the application's storage and data through the device settings.

Once the application data is removed or the application is uninstalled, all locally stored information is permanently deleted from the device.

